dict.string: Thomas needed a way to load the jobi wood onto flatbeds. Luckily, he spotted an old machine. “That’s Hee Haw,” said Dash. “He’s the old log-loading machine.” “He needs too much oil,” Bash added. “That’s why we don’t use him.” Thomas wasn’t worried. They poured the last of the oil into Hee Haw.
